{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1402254, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只有北医三院和同仁。耳朵必须同仁。五官科不要去野鸡医院（包括协和）", "timestamp": 1617716182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402265, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "打校医院电话咨询", "timestamp": 1617716219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402271, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz今早校医院检查以后开了北医三院的转诊单，但三院现在不能输液也没有空床位了，后面跑安贞医院去了也不行，再后来又托朋友联系到了别的医院，真的是太难了……", "timestamp": 1617716251, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402318, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哇那别的医院只能自费了是吗……", "timestamp": 1617716440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402337, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 其他医院急诊貌似有办法报销，需要问一下校医院的医生", "timestamp": 1617716617, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402366, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 去同仁啊……", "timestamp": 1617716862, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402401, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "听alice的，突聋不及时治会有后遗症", "timestamp": 1617717103, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402437, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哪怕你去同仁挂急诊，也还是有希望报销的。别的野鸡医院，No！", "timestamp": 1617717449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我联系的是北京友谊医院，感觉同仁大概率也没床位吧，我明天再问一下。确实就是考虑到要及时治疗所以才托关系赶紧联系上了……", "timestamp": 1617717577, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "友谊医院没问题吧，也是三甲来着", "timestamp": 1617717648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402499, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不行，不是专科医院hhh", "timestamp": 1617717850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402506, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你今晚就可以去同仁看啊……或者明早同仁特需，才500。不知道你到底是想花公家的钱还是想治好病😭", "timestamp": 1617717903, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402587, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "之前去过同仁的急诊，好像并不接诊突聋（对此我也至今很震惊）。我也是突聋患者，已经治疗一段时间了，dz有需要的话可以联系我聊聊，wx: 18811738037", "timestamp": 1617718368, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402590, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "听Alice的，急诊应该可以报。", "timestamp": 1617718383, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402675, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 对，我今天也是三院急诊，不接突聋", "timestamp": 1617719165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我是想治好病，实在不能报销也没关系，现在就是想尽快住院治疗，有些药只有住院能用。", "timestamp": 1617719314, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果医院属于学校报销范围的话，可以先住院治疗，之后再补转诊单", "timestamp": 1617719454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402727, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就同仁，明天上午，500的特需号，求求了。", "timestamp": 1617719679, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果报销不便建议直接自费，突发性耳聋需要尽快治疗，因为想报销而错过最佳治疗时间你会非常后悔的", "timestamp": 1617720202, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱dz 你以前有什么不良用耳习惯吗", "timestamp": 1617720227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402776, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "急诊、医院的事情大家已经说完了，我补充一点个人经历吧\n\n#\n\n就是我高中也有突然性右耳聋+轻微耳鸣，然后非常急地跑去医院，结果开单耵聍堵塞\n\n#\n\n希望dz没事", "timestamp": 1617720228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: dz去年暑假也有耵聍堵塞导致的听力下降，所以上周五出现症状也没太在意，以为还是耳屎满了（甚至做梦梦到医生掏耳朵掏出长条状异物hhhh）。结果今早一查没有耵聍，瞬间就慌了，手里什么活都推完了，全力治疗……", "timestamp": 1617720399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 呜呜airpods经常带，平常玩游戏也基本带入耳式耳机，然后周末经常熬夜打游戏，最近睡眠质量也比较差……\ndy们也要好好爱护自己的身体哇，dz要先跑路了！", "timestamp": 1617720511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402819, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 明白了，谢谢hans，谢谢dy们", "timestamp": 1617720538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 嗯，那就挺需要看医生了，我是右耳会这样，所以过很长一段时间我听不清之后就会滴耳液处理\n\n#\n\n祝dz健康", "timestamp": 1617720572, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402874, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 呜呜谢谢Alice关心，同仁的所有号都无了。目前看来dz只有友谊医院这个选择了。", "timestamp": 1617721078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不是哦，特需不用网上挂号，现场挂的应该是我记得？", "timestamp": 1617721165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402902, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 好吧我再了解一下情况，谢谢Alice！", "timestamp": 1617721284, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1403131, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz赶紧挂号治疗， 找好一点的三甲医院专家号，家里有亲人之前是这样的症状，一开始耽误了治疗，后来住院专家会诊只治回来了一只耳朵", "timestamp": 1617722932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1404226, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 谢谢kate，dz早起要去跑检查了，冲！我可以的！", "timestamp": 1617749154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1405697, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz好些了吗，祝早日康复", "timestamp": 1617771417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1411540, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "早日康复！！", "timestamp": 1617816488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1412369, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 275192, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: Hans得了神经性耳鸣 所以看到关于耳朵的病症都希望尽快治疗不留遗憾", "timestamp": 1617852198, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 29, "pid": 275192, "reply": 33, "tag": null, "text": "dz卑微求助……\ndz今天在校医院查出突发性耳聋，现在右边耳朵几乎听不见了，还伴随着耳鸣，非常之难受，可能马上就要住院治疗了。今天几经波折跑了三家医院终于联系上一家医院有空床位，想问一下咱们学生的公费医疗是只能在北医三院报销吗？还是说有可报销的医院范围？\n以及一定要开了转院单才能去治疗吗？来不及开转院单了能不能先住院治疗，之后再回学校补？", "timestamp": 1617716118, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617852197, "url": "", "vote": {}}}